						               													<description>In a mysterious coffee shop, customers are asking for the song they want to hear now. Let's become &amp;quot;Meisters&amp;quot; who work in coffee shops, select the right songs that customers want, and play them!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;120 songs from 120 artists can be selected as cards by Record Meister! The selection genres range from pop music that everyone knows to rock, classic, jazz, reggae, Latin, fusion, metal, EDM, techno, game music, movie music, bokaro, and so on. There is no doubt that you will encounter new music through the game that you have never heard before.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each turn, one player will play as the customer while the others will be the &amp;quot;Meisters&amp;quot;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The customer draw a topic card, chooses one topic on the card and announces it to the meisters.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Then, all the meisters start looking for a song among the vinyl cards on the table.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each meister plays the song he selected (using a QR code on the card) and explains how the song matches the topic.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Once all the meisters have talked, the customer selects the best song and the selected meister get 1 point (keeping the vinyl card).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Play several rounds. The most points at the end of the game wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
